attributeValues.value: Retro styled and easy to use, the KitchenAid Artisan stand mixer is the perfect kitchen companion. Employing a unique tilting head to facilitate bowl and content removal, this mixer is undeniably handy. 1-year hassle-free replacement warranty. Model KSM150PS.
Includes flat beater, wire whip, dough hook, pouring shield and 5-qt. polished bowl with ergonomic handles
Powerful 325-watt motor effectively mixes even the toughest dough and batter
Pouring shield reduces mess by channeling ingredients into bowl
You can return this item to any Macy's store within 60 days from purchase date. Last Act items must be returned within 30 days from purchase date.
